---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about who I am, what I do, and how to get in touch."
>
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>
      Hi! I'm the person behind <strong>naiveI</strong>. I'm a developer who
      enjoys building things for the web.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Do</h2>
    <p>
      I work with modern web technologies to build fast, accessible, and
      delightful user experiences. My interests span front-end development,
      static site generators, and developer tooling.
    </p>

    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>JavaScript / TypeScript</li>
      <li>HTML &amp; CSS</li>
      <li>Astro, React, and other frameworks</li>
      <li>Git &amp; CI/CD</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      You can find me on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      and <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>,
      or reach out via email at <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
